## About Me

I am an Assistant Professor in the Department of Mathematics at TKM College of Engineering, Kollam. I hold a Ph.D. in Mathematics from the National Institute of Technology Calicut. My academic interests include fuzzy set theory, hesitant fuzzy sets, rough sets, and their applications.

